@0 = ~Hello! I come from Neverwinter for help. A plague is rampant in my city and it is clearly not of natural origin. Lady Aribeth and Lord Nasher have sent me to Ascathla to find heroes to help Neverwinter. Perhaps you can help.~/*是的，我是从无冬城来的。 这瘟疫是个礼物，能控制他，那有多好！ 艾瑞贝丝以及纳什尔领主要我调查这里。 或许我可以帮忙？*/
@1 = ~I'm not interested. Find someone else.~/*我没兴趣。 “问别人吧。”*/
@2 = ~Well, I guess I'll try to help. Where is this city located?~/*真的吗？我想我会去的！ 主塔在哪里？*/
@3 = ~It's north of Athkatla. If you agree to help, I will teleport you to Lady Aribeth at the Neverwinter Academy.~/*这不关我的事。 你是对的。我会在你父亲的农场和你见面。*/
@4 = ~Not now.~/*不是现在！*/
@5 = ~Yes, I'm ready.~/*是的，准备好了。*/
@6 = ~Well, I'll be waiting for you here.~/*这，这让我们无所适从。*/
@7 = ~Then get ready, now you will find yourself in the Neverwinter Academy. Lady Aribeth will explain everything to you in detail.~/*这只狗希望你能够好好地教训那些侵略者。 不，但无论如何我都会拿走你尸体上的任何东西。*/
@8 = ~You're back. Does that mean you're going to help us?~
/*你完蛋了！ 你不是要来帮助我的吗？*/